125
00:06:55,950 --> 00:06:56,750
Why?

126
00:06:58,510 --> 00:06:59,159
Since fates

127
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,600
have started to change,

128
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,160
maybe you

129
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:04,090
