140
00:07:48,310 --> 00:07:50,310
Don't worry. Two days.

141
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:52,010
Just give me two days.

142
00:07:52,510 --> 00:07:53,800
Once the buzz dies down,

143
00:07:53,870 --> 00:07:55,210
I promise I'll get him out.

144
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,190
Why were the reporters there?

145
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,070
An anonymous letter.

146
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,640
Lai.

147
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,120
It must be Lai.

148
00:08:09,950 --> 00:08:11,980
I know you have a grudge with Lai.

149
00:08:12,010 --> 00:08:12,750
But

150
00:08:12,750 --> 00:08:14,630
