152
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,770
Investigate it.

153
00:08:18,950 --> 00:08:19,870
Get me evidence.

154
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,240
If it was him,

155
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:22,630
