186
00:10:35,790 --> 00:10:36,680
Dead?

187
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:37,540
Yes.

188
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,120
How did he die?

189
00:10:39,170 --> 00:10:39,920
He hung himself.

190
00:10:39,940 --> 00:10:41,120
