409
00:24:33,670 --> 00:24:34,350
Lily.

410
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:37,010
I think

411
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:38,940
it doesn't matter how long you get

412
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:40,760
to be with the one you love.

413
00:24:41,160 --> 00:24:42,350
What matters

414
00:24:42,830 --> 00:24:44,690
