417
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:02,320
I went to get some fresh air.

418
00:25:02,440 --> 00:25:04,300
It's too stuffy in the house.

419
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:05,310
Here.

420
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:06,240
Put it on.

421
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,450
What is this?

422
00:25:11,020 --> 00:25:12,410
I ran out of medicine.

423
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:13,980
I went out to buy some.

424
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:15,510
Mr. Bai Lang.

425
00:25:15,750 --> 00:25:17,250
Just hang in there a while more.

426
00:25:17,400 --> 00:25:18,950
A miracle drug will be released soon.

427
00:25:20,310 --> 00:25:21,480
A miracle drug?

428
00:25:22,550 --> 00:25:23,490
Yes.

429
00:25:25,230 --> 00:25:27,190
