433
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,270
Yes.

434
00:25:36,350 --> 00:25:37,000
Bai Lang.

435
00:25:47,720 --> 00:25:48,270
Jia!

436
00:25:48,920 --> 00:25:49,550
Jia!

437
00:25:49,910 --> 00:25:51,790
Lai found a photo of Rou killing Liu Meng.

438
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,640
Now Chief Inspector Zhang knows everything.

439
00:25:53,660 --> 00:25:54,720
He wants to see you.

440
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:57,240
Jia.

441
00:26:12,030 --> 00:26:12,590
Zhao.

442
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,990
How do I usually treat you?

443
00:26:15,050 --> 00:26:16,960
Jia, you're always very nice to me.

444
00:26:17,510 --> 00:26:18,160
This time,

445
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:20,590
I need you to do me a favor.

446
00:26:24,110 --> 00:26:25,160
For Liu Meng's case,

447
00:26:26,110 --> 00:26:27,870
who ordered Weilun

448
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:29,450
to frame Lai?

449
00:26:29,700 --> 00:26:30,620
Frame?

450
00:26:34,590 --> 00:26:35,230
Zhao.

451
00:26:36,820 --> 00:26:38,260
Weren't you monitoring

452
00:26:38,420 --> 00:26:39,930
Zhang Weilun's case?

453
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:41,590
Spit it out!

454
00:26:43,350 --> 00:26:44,230
It was me.

455
00:26:44,720 --> 00:26:46,590
Weilun was worried that if the investigation continued,

456
00:26:46,610 --> 00:26:48,080
Rou's identity would be exposed.

457
00:26:48,510 --> 00:26:50,240
So he said he killed Liu Meng.

458
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,770
He knew Lai would find out the truth,

459
00:26:53,550 --> 00:26:55,250
so he bribed me

460
00:26:55,680 --> 00:26:56,700
to frame Lai.

461
00:26:58,230 --> 00:26:59,450
Zhao's misdeed must be

462
00:26:59,710 --> 00:27:00,900
dealt with strictly.

463
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,480
Reinstate

464
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,830
Lai today.

465
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:04,590
Also,

466
00:27:04,750 --> 00:27:05,830
once Rou wakes up,

467
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:06,690
