470
00:27:43,830 --> 00:27:45,200
The truth of Liu Meng's case is revealed.

471
00:27:46,150 --> 00:27:48,080
The person who framed me is under investigation,

472
00:27:48,110 --> 00:27:50,430
and Rou will be arrested when she wakes up.

473
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:51,640
What about you?

474
00:27:52,020 --> 00:27:53,930
I'll go back to being a cop, of course.

475
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:55,470
What about you?

476
00:27:55,790 --> 00:27:56,920
Have you found the lighter?

477
00:27:57,160 --> 00:27:58,880
Of course I did.

478
00:27:59,550 --> 00:28:00,960
After I got the lighter,

479
00:28:01,070 --> 00:28:02,820
I even met an old couple

480
00:28:02,920 --> 00:28:04,480
