484
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:11,580
Share it with me.

485
00:28:11,790 --> 00:28:12,640
You've seen it.

486
00:28:17,270 --> 00:28:18,070
He has a knife!

487
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,830
Murder! Murder!

488
00:28:20,130 --> 00:28:20,820
Bing?

489
00:28:20,890 --> 00:28:21,640
It's Bing!

490
00:28:21,670 --> 00:28:23,190
It's your fault that Bing was arrested.

491
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,520
He killed you!

492
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:25,480
Watch out!

493
00:28:26,050 --> 00:28:27,680
I must avenge Bing!

494
00:28:35,070 --> 00:28:35,850
Lai!

495
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:42,950
You framed Bing.

496
00:28:43,200 --> 00:28:44,500
You caught the wrong person!

497
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:46,350
I must avenge my son!

498
00:28:46,830 --> 00:28:47,680
Bing is innocent.

499
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,410
Lai!

500
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:51,310
I must kill you. I must kill you!

501
00:28:54,550 --> 00:28:55,170
Lai.

502
00:28:57,280 --> 00:28:58,080
Watch out!

503
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:01,750
