00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:15,590
Are you okay now?

551
00:31:17,310 --> 00:31:18,300
I'm fine.

552
00:31:19,190 --> 00:31:20,320
Excuse me.

553
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:22,230
